{# An AI / sub-agent text message rendered as safe HTML. The body
   comes pre-rendered from ``render_markdown`` (CommonMark + linkify,
   raw-HTML disabled), so we mark it ``|safe`` to skip Jinja's
   autoescape. The wrapper class lets CSS apply markdown-element
   styling (headings, code, lists, …) without leaking those styles
   into other log entries.

   ctx:
     html  — pre-rendered HTML from render_markdown
#}
<div class="log-entry log-ai ai-message">{{ html|safe }}</div>
